Labyrinth-Plugin-Requests
=========================

This distribution contains the request handling functionality for the Labyrinth
Web Framework. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these modules:

  Labyrinth

For testing the module requires these modules:

  IO::File
  Test::More

For optional testing the module would like these modules:

  Test::CPAN::Meta
  Test::CPAN::Meta::JSON
  Test::Pod
  Test::Pod::Coverage

